column6:
This apartment is: 
* Just outside NW Austin city limits in Cedar Park
* Convenient to all things Austin
* Minutes from Lake Travis
* Located a few minutes from the Austin Metro Rail
* In an area where Uber and Lyft are available! 
* Walking distance to local parks, restaurants and dining
* Down the street from one of the area's largest malls
* A popular place because of location 
* Good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers
* FREE WIFI
column9: Comfy NW Austin Suburb Apt near Metro Rail to Aus
